cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about improving the U-Net architecture for medical image segmentation, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes modifications to the U-Net architecture, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG, cs.AI). The focus of the paper is on multimodal biomedical image segmentation, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the performance gains achieved through the proposed modifications, which suggests the use of neural networks (cs.NE).
